## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Unit test session persistence: start → serialize → reload → verify all fields restored
- Unit test SVD re-parse on session restore
- Unit test firmware system prompt generation with various MCU configs
- Integration: project auto-detect → session start → SVD load → verify context injection contains registers

### Manual Verification
- Open a real STM32 project → verify auto-detection → check Power Mode agent knows the MCU
- Connect a serial device → verify serial monitor shows data → verify agent can read serial output
- Build a PlatformIO project → verify build output parsing → verify agent reports errors
- Flash a device → verify flash tool detection → verify agent confirms success
